## Faraday's Law of Induction

### Integral Form:

$$
\oint_{\partial \mathcal{C}} \mathbf{E} \cdot d\mathbf{l} = -\frac{d}{dt} \iint_{\mathcal{S}} \mathbf{B} \cdot d\mathbf{A}
$$

### Differential Form:

$$
\nabla \times \mathbf{E} = -\frac{\partial \mathbf{B}}{\partial t}
$$

